Describe linux/debian安装wn722n(ath9k-htc) here.
----

 1. Add a "non-free" component to /etc/apt/sources.list, for example:
{{{
# Debian 7.0 "Wheezy"
deb http://http.debian.net/debian/ wheezy main contrib non-free
}}}
 1. Update the list of available packages and install the firmware-atheros package:
{{{
# apt-get update && apt-get install firmware-atheros
}}}
 1. Connect the device to your system. The ath9k_htc kernel module is automatically loaded for supported devices.

 1. Configure your wireless interface as appropriate. 

更多相关：[[http://wiki.debian.org/ath9k_htc]]
